1
00:01:09,040 --> 00:01:10,320
They kicked me,

2
00:01:10,960 --> 00:01:11,840
one kick,

3
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:13,720
two kicks,

4
00:01:15,240 --> 00:01:16,160
three kicks...

5
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,840
Until one day,

6
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:28,040
the enemy suddenly had to retreat.

7
00:01:28,520 --> 00:01:29,440
They took me,

8
00:01:29,440 --> 00:01:30,360
this half-dead,

9
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:31,760
useless piece of trash,

10
00:01:32,760 --> 00:01:34,320
and threw me into the deep woods,

11
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:35,840
leaving me for the wild beasts

12
00:01:36,160 --> 00:01:36,840
to tear apart.

13
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:39,400
Fortunately, heaven had mercy.

14
00:01:40,800 --> 00:01:42,440
A Taoist Master saved me.

15
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:45,200
From then on,

16
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,520
I became a disciple

17
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:49,400
of the Guigu School

18
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,840
and became Yihe.

19
00:01:54,920 --> 00:01:55,680
What happened next?

20
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:58,720
Later...

21
00:02:00,720 --> 00:02:03,160
Later, while wandering the world,

22
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:06,240
I returned to my hometown.

23
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:09,880
From the neighbors, I learned

24
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:13,160
that the murderer of my family

25
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:16,520
was your father,

26
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:19,240
Huang Zhenyue.

27
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:24,040
He was afraid the enemy

28
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:26,120
would use my family to force me

29
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,320
to reveal military secrets.

30
00:02:28,320 --> 00:02:29,760
So he killed my family

31
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,840
to eliminate the risk.

32
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:34,760
But he...

33
00:02:35,760 --> 00:02:36,840
He did it to defeat the enemy.

34
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,040
So he had no choice but to do it.

35
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,520
Those are just your father's excuses!

36
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:41,600
He could have

37
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:42,880
protected my family.

38
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,480
He could have

39
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:45,760
hidden my family.

40
00:02:46,160 --> 00:02:47,120
But he didn't.

41
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:49,120
He didn't do that.

42
00:02:50,520 --> 00:02:52,040
There is only one reason.

43
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:53,960
And that is,

44
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:55,680
he never trusted me.

45
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:57,400
Never.

46
00:02:58,040 --> 00:02:58,960
So,

47
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:01,400
when you learned the truth,

48
00:03:02,880 --> 00:03:04,480
you decided to take revenge.

49
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,120
Even Qingqing,

50
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:08,120
you deliberately took her in,

51
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:14,120
just so on the day we married,

52
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,240
you could strike.

53
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:16,120
Is that right?

54
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,120
Yes.

55
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:18,960
That's right.

56
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:20,640
A year ago,

57
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,240
at your wedding with Qingqing,

58
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:25,560
I caught Su Yao alone

59
00:03:26,240 --> 00:03:27,520
and killed your mother first.

60
00:03:28,400 --> 00:03:29,440
Later,

61
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:32,200
I tried to kill Huang Zhenyue too.

62
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:33,520
I didn't expect

63
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,400
him to react so fast,

64
00:03:36,120 --> 00:03:37,280
which ruined my plan.

65
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,640
I had no choice

66
00:03:40,680 --> 00:03:41,800
but to stop.

67
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,120
A year later,

68
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:47,360
using the name Liu Jiaquan,

69
00:03:49,080 --> 00:03:50,520
I asked your father

70
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:54,240
to meet at the pier warehouse.

71
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:13,960
Jiaquan

72
00:04:23,520 --> 00:04:24,280
Commander Huang

73
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:26,960
Long time no see.

74
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:30,800
This is great, Jiaquan.

75
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:33,080
I didn't expect you to still be alive.

76
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:34,640
This is great.

77
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:39,840
Jiaquan.

78
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:42,000
Back then, I searched the entire enemy camp,

79
00:04:42,360 --> 00:04:43,240
but I couldn't find you.

80
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:44,560
I thought you were already...

81
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:48,000
That I came back alive,

82
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:51,640
are you feeling particularly surprised, Commander Huang?

83
00:04:52,280 --> 00:04:52,840
Yes.

84
00:04:53,520 --> 00:04:54,800
I feel particularly happy.

85
00:04:55,520 --> 00:04:55,960
Jiaquan,

86
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:57,200
come home with me.

87
00:04:58,080 --> 00:04:59,200
Let's have a drink, brother.

88
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,400
Let's go.

89
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:02,840
Huang Zhenyue.

90
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:07,000
I treated you like my own brother,

91
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:09,080
my good older brother.

92
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:12,720
Yet you killed my entire family.

93
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:16,240
Even my pregnant wife,

94
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:18,440
you didn't spare her.

95
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,440
Jiaquan,

96
00:05:28,640 --> 00:05:30,000
we are both soldiers.

97
00:05:30,440 --> 00:05:31,880
You know the situation back then.

98
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,880
The enemy was in hot pursuit.

99
00:05:34,400 --> 00:05:35,560
If I hadn't done that,

100
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:37,120
once the military intel leaked...

101
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,200
Do you know

102
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:40,200
how many soldiers would have died?

103
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,880
How many families would have been broken?

104
00:05:44,400 --> 00:05:46,000
I had no other choice.

105
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:50,640
No other choice?

106
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:53,200
What a convenient excuse.

107
00:05:55,000 --> 00:05:57,000
As the saying goes, leave the family out of it.

108
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:58,880
Let me ask you,

109
00:06:01,640 --> 00:06:03,080
my elderly father

110
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:04,680
and mother...

111
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:07,640
They couldn't harm a fly.

112
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:10,120
What crime did they commit?

113
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,080
And my...

114
00:06:13,080 --> 00:06:14,520
pregnant wife,

115
00:06:16,080 --> 00:06:17,640
my unborn child...

116
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:19,680
What did they do wrong?

117
00:06:22,880 --> 00:06:23,840
Huang Zhenyue,

118
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:27,320
how could you actually bring yourself to do it?

119
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:39,080
I will use your blood

120
00:06:39,640 --> 00:06:41,320
to pay tribute to my family.

121
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:49,120
This is what you deserve.

122
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,880
Even death is too good for you.

123
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,880
As for what happened next,

124
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:03,400
I don't think I need

125
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:04,640
to explain it piece by piece.

126
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:06,880
But why did you

127
00:07:07,640 --> 00:07:09,000
have to kill my cousin?

128
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:10,640
That's because his surname is Huang.

129
00:07:11,960 --> 00:07:14,120
I want to kill everyone in the Huang family.

130
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:16,960
Only by killing everyone

131
00:07:16,960 --> 00:07:18,080
in your Huang family

132
00:07:18,880 --> 00:07:20,880
can I relieve the hatred in my heart.

133
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:29,680
What about Ba Gu?

134
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:32,080
She has no blood relation to us at all.

135
00:07:32,080 --> 00:07:33,440
Why did you kill her?

136
00:07:34,200 --> 00:07:35,000
Ba Gu...

137
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,760
I originally wanted to use her to kill you.

138
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:40,080
But I didn't expect

139
00:07:41,120 --> 00:07:42,640
you to be so lucky.

140
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:44,880
You actually managed to escape.

141
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:46,440
Therefore,

142
00:07:47,320 --> 00:07:48,880
keeping her alive was of no use.

143
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,200
What about You Tong?

144
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:54,560
What's your relationship with her?

145
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:57,560
She was just a little girl

146
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:59,440
who wanted to be my disciple.

147
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:01,520
I saw she had good potential,

148
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:04,400
so I just wanted to use her.

149
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,640
Do you think doing this

150
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:08,320
will soothe your hatred?

151
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:10,200
You've killed so many people.

152
00:08:11,240 --> 00:08:11,960
Have you ever thought

153
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,680
that they also have their own families,

154
00:08:14,320 --> 00:08:15,320
and their own lives?

155
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,680
I only want revenge.

156
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,440
I only know

157
00:08:19,080 --> 00:08:20,320
that I must make your Huang family

158
00:08:20,760 --> 00:08:22,080
pay blood for blood.

159
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:23,760
You have been blinded

160
00:08:24,760 --> 00:08:25,760
by your hatred.

161
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:27,000
By doing this,

162
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:28,560
how are you any different

163
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,440
from those cruel enemy troops?

164
00:08:31,400 --> 00:08:32,320
I don't know.

165
00:08:33,680 --> 00:08:34,640
I only know that

166
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,640
from the moment

167
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:38,000
your father killed my whole family,

168
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,200
from that very instant,

169
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:41,400
the old Liu Jiaquan

170
00:08:41,400 --> 00:08:42,640
was already dead.

171
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:47,200
The Yihe who lives now

172
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,400
exists only for revenge.

173
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:50,560
Revenge!

174
00:08:51,760 --> 00:08:53,880
I will kill everyone in your Huang family!

175
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,240
It's a pity

176
00:09:05,760 --> 00:09:07,640
that the current Yihe

177
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,760
is also dead.

178
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:16,080
Inspector,

179
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:19,920
has the verdict been reached?

180
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:22,440
Liu Jiaquan is guilty of Murder

181
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:23,480
and sentenced to death,

182
00:10:23,680 --> 00:10:24,280
to be executed immediately.

183
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:25,680
You Tong is an accomplice

184
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:26,960
and was sentenced to ten years.

185
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,160
Those who break the law

186
00:10:29,560 --> 00:10:30,960
will surely be severely punished by it.

187
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,080
It's just a pity

188
00:10:32,840 --> 00:10:34,160
that the people they brutally murdered

189
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:35,600
will never come back.

190
00:10:38,920 --> 00:10:39,960
What about my uncles?

191
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:42,080
How are they doing?

192
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:44,560
The appointment for Jiangyu City's

193
00:10:44,560 --> 00:10:46,080
new Supreme Marshal

194
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:46,840
has already been issued.

195
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:47,960
General Ling and his men

196
00:10:48,160 --> 00:10:49,600
probably received the news early.

197
00:10:49,800 --> 00:10:50,680
They already evacuated last night.

198
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:00,440
Jinrong,

199
00:11:02,280 --> 00:11:03,320
are you really willing to give up

200
00:11:03,960 --> 00:11:05,440
the appointment as Supreme Marshal?

201
00:11:14,080 --> 00:11:14,960
I just want to restore

202
00:11:15,960 --> 00:11:17,120
peace to Jiangyu City.
